HEADWORD: glossina
<hw>glossina</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A blood-sucking African fly that
transmits sleeping sickness etc.; the tsetse fly.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> tsetse fly, tsetse, tzetze fly, tzetze.</syn>⟦br⟧
